=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Je6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=714e2982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"704d11721ce6984e869547155d2fee00f4060c0b","tid":2076592,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Je6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=8daacfcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Je6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=fcde04a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"d4d119f29f4a038e58bbdffc0f9e3f51f1943244","tid":2076592,"uid":292499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NQuJVN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NQuJVN.jpg&h=a1cc9482&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46473ae84af4708bc4c6b35ddd10a83f202e80f4","tid":2076592,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接