76592,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb24984b971eb9cc7967a899cede609c22f9664b","tid":2076592,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />法庭聲援要人"},{"pid":"e5026358d784629e6547e6da7deeadafe20ba6d6","tid":2076592,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"#街坊投搞<br />\n<br />\n‼️有手足要坐12日冤獄‼️<br />\n 香淑嫻裁判官嘅判決太過份🤬<br />\n相關案例最多3千而家起碼坐12日，但無乜人關注~ 請spread ❗️<br />\n<br />\n學生11月11日喺柴灣天橋上被截查搜出背囊內有摺刀被控藏有違禁武器<br />\n<br />\n1. 控方改「摺刀」為「彈簧刀」 , 庭上將「違禁武器專家」 轉為「彈簧刀專家」<br />\n<br />\n2. 而該專家庭上認同辯方律師指自己並非違禁武器專家，但法庭仍接納證人為違禁武器專家。<br />\n<br />\n3. 被搜出刀後第一時間解釋刀嘅用途係生火，裁判官因被告無庭上作供就全不考慮。<br />\n<br />\n4. 被告患有過度活躍症及專注力不足，個性善忙，年紀又輕(18歲)，但裁判官沒有考慮此求情。<br />\n<br />\n5. 裁判官試圖用非案情內嘅事嚟做判刑理據，其後被辯方律師指出不在案情內，裁判官最終收回。<br />\n<br />\n6. 辯方提供4個相關案例，最重只判罰$3000, 但被告需還押12日候判。<br />\n<br />\n詳情睇：<br />\n審訊- 蘋果 頭條<br />\n裁決- 蘋果 立場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/chaisiuhanginfo/13968\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fchaisiuhanginfo%2F13968&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Je6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=b3f1c113\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/chaisiuhanginfo/13968</a>"},{"pid":"8f18bd6f0f94c2b08617e1e46306ad20fc033e1a","tid":2076592,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"另外高院5樓7庭天日10：30有幾宗司法覆核案開始聆訊"},{"pid":"ccfd6fa356459bd033827a